## Skills System

Harness-OS features a tiered skill system to help you perform task-specific functions:
1. **Always Loaded (Tier 1)** (Auto-loaded on start): `harness-workflow` (core RIPER-5), `karpathy-guidelines` (thinking and simplicity), `strategic-compact` (context-window optimization). Stack baselines: `csharp-baseline` (dotnet), `php-baseline` (php).
2. **Auto-Suggested (Tier 2)** (Suggested based on task keywords; load recommended ones with score >= 1.5): `tdd-workflow` (test-driven development), `systematic-diagnosis` (structured debugging), `code-review-workflow` (self-review checklist before merge), `read-first` (read and understand first), `verification-loop` (verify loop during coding).
3. **On-Demand (Tier 3)** (Load explicitly when needed): `write-a-skill` (how to write new skills).

### How to Combine Skills

Use the formula: **`[Tier-1 Core] + [Stack Baseline] + [Task-Type] + [Add-ons]`**

| Loại task | Công thức |
|-----------|-----------|
| Tính năng mới C# | `harness-workflow` + `csharp-baseline` + `csharp-feature` + `tdd-workflow` |
| Fix bug C# | `harness-workflow` + `csharp-baseline` + `systematic-diagnosis` + `csharp-bugfix` (+ `csharp-repair` nếu có compile/test errors) |
| Fix bug PHP CI4 | `harness-workflow` + `php-baseline` + `systematic-diagnosis` + `php-codeigniter-4-workflow` |
| Code review C# | `harness-workflow` + `code-review-workflow` + `csharp-code-review` |
| Code review general | `harness-workflow` + `code-review-workflow` |
| Thiết kế tính năng | `harness-workflow` + `brainstorming` → (sau khi chọn approach) → `design-grilling` |

